//Write a program to find the greatest element in an arrayâ€¦

int main()
{
    int max,n,i,a[10];
    printf("\n enter n:");
    scanf("%d",&n);
    for(i=0;i<n;i++)
    {
        printf("\n element at a[%d]:",i);
        scanf("%d",&a[i]);
    }
    max=a[0];
    for(i=1;i<n;i++)
    {
        if(a[i]>max)
            max=a[i];
    }
    printf("\n maximum=%d",max);
}


Output:

enter n:5
 element at a[0]:8
 element at a[1]:5
 element at a[2]:4
 element at a[3]:7
 element at a[4]:6
 maximum=8

Reference:https://funcodepro.blogspot.com/2018/12/how-to-find-greatest-element.html
